    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model for the Class III VAD device demonstrates sufficient credibility for regulatory submission. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides confidence in the hemolysis index predictions across the five operating points. The model is accepted for use in the intended context.",
